<h2>ABOUT</h2>
<h3>Montgomery Real Estate Market</h3>
<p>Montgomery is located in both ward 1 and 7, is represented by Dale Hodges and Druh Farrell respectively. Provincially, Montgomery is located in the Calgary-Bow riding, represented by Alana Delong and federally in the Calgary West riding, represented by Ron Anders.</p>
<p>Montgomery homes are mostly made up of residential attached and detached single-family (bungalow, two storey), which make up around 71.8% of the market, with the remaining 28.2% being apartments and condominiums.</p>
<p>Approximately 37.9% of homes are occupied by rental tenants. These figures come from statistics gathered in 2006, and may not be completely accurate to the current state of the community.</p>
</div>
